 Added Textinput_Styles gadget for using other Types of Display.
 Fixed a bug that wouldn't let you add a clip more than 1000 chars long.
 Changed the list handling routines for cleaner updating.
 Fixed 'Get New Version' Function.
 Changed using '%n' to 'Ctrl_C n' (the colour prefix + n)

