 Completed the Clipper.cs file for transtations

 Version 5.3 / 5.4

 Asl File Requester would not work for someone ??? so i made Clipper use MUI
 asl functions

 Version 5.2

 Fixed a bug in QuickEdit String gadget so changes get sent to clipboard
 Thanks to Michael Hendren for pointing that one out :)

 Version 5.1
 QuickChange String gadget can now be hidden
 ARexx functions Added:  LOAD, SAVE,  GET or SET (config items)

 Version 5.0
 It's here at last :) Clipper MUI
 Now uses Textinput_mcc for editing so colour codes are viewable plus it's a
 multiline gadget so real Editor like editing is now possible

 now we can use all MUI's handy features like setting PubScreen,
 snapshot windows, completely configure the look of GUI,
 alt tab window cycling,iconify, ect, ect

 ClipUnit can be changed

 Image gadgets can be Hidden/moved

