@node rexx "Clipper Arexx functions"

                    @{b} WARNING @{ub} Document Unfinished :-\\

                               Clipper ARexx Port

     Please note: i only added the ARexx port because i did not know how to
       add commands to an MUI app, so these functions are pretty useless.


Clipper's ARexx port starts as CLIPPER.1 and then CLIPPER.2 and so on

To address the port you MUST use the 'ADDRESS VALUE' method
eg.

ADDRESS VALUE CLIPPER.1


COMMANDS:

LOAD   AS/S   loads current settings, use AS to load via Requester
SAVE   AS/S   saves current settings, use AS to save via Requester

GET    CONFIG/S,PAGENAME/S,PAGENUM/S  get settings information

SET    CONFIG/S,PAGENAME/S.PAGENUM/S,DATA/F  Sets a parameter with data

----
an example of how to get the settings file name..

/**/
ADDRESS VALUE CLIPPER.1
GET CONFIG
say RESULT

----

an example of how to load a new settings file..

/**/
ADDRESS VALUE CLIPPER.1
SET CONFIG ClipperIRC.cfg
LOAD


@endnode
